OL,3,C'Register4Ronnie': Urgent stem cell
OL,4,Cplea for baby boy with rare blood
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThe mother of a baby boy diagnosed
OL,8,Fwith a rare blood condition a week
OL,9,Fbefore his first birthday is urging
OL,10,Fpeople to join the stem cell register
OL,11,Fin the hopes of curing her son.
OL,13,FRonnie, from Merseyside, had just
OL,14,Fstarted crawling when his mother Laura
OL,15,Fnoticed he was bruising more.
OL,17,FThe one-year-old was eventually
OL,18,Fdiagnosed with aplastic anaemia, which
OL,19,Fis fatal if left untreated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
