CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775005383
OL,3,C'Register4Ronnie': Urgent stem cell
OL,4,Cplea for baby boy with rare blood
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FIt happens when the bone marrow cannot
OL,8,Fmake enough new blood cells for the
OL,9,Fbody to work normally, with around 100
OL,10,Fto 150 new cases in the UK every year.
OL,12,FLaura, 30, said: "He had only just
OL,13,Fstarted crawling, then three days
OL,14,Flater when I got him up, he had blood
OL,15,Fcoming from his nose, blisters in his
OL,16,Fmouth, and red dots on his body."
OL,18,FRonnie was rushed to hospital where
OL,19,Fmedics initially suspected he had
OL,20,Fleukaemia, a type of blood cancer.
OL,26,@tD@ROUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775005383
OL,3,C'Register4Ronnie': Urgent stem cell
OL,4,Cplea for baby boy with rare blood
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FHe was then taken to Alder Hey
OL,8,FChildren's Hospital in Liverpool for
OL,9,Fblood and platelet transfusions.
OL,11,F"The room went quiet, our hearts were
OL,12,Fpounding, and then instantly our minds
OL,13,Fwere jumping to the worst-case
OL,14,Fscenario and thinking how is my 11-
OL,15,Fmonth-old meant to battle such a
OL,16,Fdeadly disease at such a young age,"
OL,17,FLaura said.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775005383
OL,3,C'Register4Ronnie': Urgent stem cell
OL,4,Cplea for baby boy with rare blood
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,F"This is a day that will forever be
OL,8,Fengraved in our minds, every time we
OL,9,Fhear sirens now it takes us back to
OL,10,Fthat night of being blue lighted to
OL,11,FAlder Hey."
OL,13,FCancer was later ruled out, although
OL,14,Fdoctors were struggling to test
OL,15,FRonnie's bone marrow as it was so
OL,16,Fsparse.
OL,18,FThe family was told his levels were at
OL,19,F5% with very few cells, when a baby
OL,20,Fhis age should have 100%.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
