SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775005383
OL,3,C'Register4Ronnie': Urgent stem cell
OL,4,Cplea for baby boy with rare blood
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FA second test eventually revealed
OL,8,FRonnie had aplastic anaemia and his
OL,9,Fparents were told a bone marrow
OL,10,Ftransplant would be his only hope of a
OL,11,Fcure.
OL,13,FAplastic anaemia can affect anyone at
OL,14,Fany age, but is more common in people
OL,15,Faged between 10 and 20, and those over
OL,16,F60.
OL,18,FSymptoms include tiredness, shortness
OL,19,Fof breath, headaches, bleeding from
OL,20,Fthe nose or gums, and infections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775005383
OL,3,C'Register4Ronnie': Urgent stem cell
OL,4,Cplea for baby boy with rare blood
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FLaura said her son is still "happy and
OL,8,Fsmiling" despite having infusions and
OL,9,Finjections to stimulate his bone
OL,10,Fmarrow production.
OL,12,FHowever, there is also a worry over
OL,13,Finfections as Ronnie has been
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with neutropenia.
OL,16,FThis causes a type of white blood cell
OL,17,Fthat is essential for fighting
OL,18,Fbacterial infections to become
OL,19,Fabnormally low.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
