OL,3,C'Register4Ronnie': Urgent stem cell
OL,4,Cplea for baby boy with rare blood
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThe family is working with the charity
OL,8,FAnthony Nolan on the Register4Ronnie
OL,9,Fcampaign.
OL,11,FThey hope this will encourage more
OL,12,Fpeople to join the stem cell register
OL,13,Fto help children like Ronnie, as well
OL,14,Fas youngsters with other conditions
OL,15,Fsuch as leukaemia.
OL,17,F"Now we have adiagnosis wehave todo
OL,18,Fsomething to help," Laura said.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775005383
OL,3,C'Register4Ronnie': Urgent stem cell
OL,4,Cplea for baby boy with rare blood
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,F"There are so many other kids out
OL,8,Fthere who need a match, we are putting
OL,9,Fit out there for Ronnie and to educate
OL,10,Fpeople about the lifesaving potential
OL,11,Fof stem cell transplants.
OL,13,F"Being fromMerseyside, we all stick
OL,14,Ftogether from here.
OL,16,F"We're sharing Ronnie's story because
OL,17,Fwe want people to get tested, if a
OL,18,Fmatch comes up for him then great, but
OL,19,Fa match for someone else, that's
OL,20,Famazing as well."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
