OL,3,C'Register4Ronnie': Urgent stem cell
OL,4,Cplea for baby boy with rare blood
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FRowena Bentley, head of programme and
OL,8,Fcommunity recruitment at Anthony
OL,9,FNolan, said:"It's heartbreaking that
OL,10,Fbaby Ronnie and his family are going
OL,11,Fthrough this, and we are doing our
OL,12,Fbest to support them.
OL,14,F"At Anthony Nolan we give hope to
OL,15,Ffamilies affected by blood cancers and
OL,16,Fdisorders, but we can't do it without
OL,17,Fthe lifesavers that sign up to our
OL,18,Fregister.
OL,26,@qD@NOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
